{"tid":1699944,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"捉鬼記（歡迎巴絲提供資料）","createTime":"2019-11-08T08:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T01:59:09.000Z","uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c89c601f0efebabb993f9742d1514687d3b90604","tid":1699944,"uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:52:35.000Z","msg":"2019年11月8日<br />\n<br />\n「即時」中環青年被捕 元氣員工露出歡顏笑容<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1699893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1699893</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主用兩張唔連續既相，加無source既新聞，煽動連登巴絲裝修元氣壽司。<br />\n<br />\n冰城google後，並無正式新聞。<br />\n有理由相信該post樓主係鬼，煽動連登巴絲暴力對待錯誤的對象。<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼記：成功"},{"pid":"34b2abe24bb850fb15601acb94fa0724c40c98f5","tid":1699944,"uid":37924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:53:37.000Z","msg":"戇鳩post"},{"pid":"abfd0e98b41e0304089c09b03d97c300a2a470fa","tid":1699944,"uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"34b2abe24bb850fb15601acb94fa0724c40c98f5","tid":1699944,"uid":37924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:53:37.000Z","msg":"戇鳩post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:54:34.000Z","msg":"唔想fact check呀？<br />\n你用心惡毒呀"},{"pid":"ff7319f47dcbd5c3c42c41c3a02419d2c322edf4","tid":1699944,"uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:08:16.000Z","msg":"此post會繼續更新<br />\n<br />\n冰城成功捉鬼數目 1"},{"pid":"603bf606c49f64c1fa196c9fae03fe09c8c00d7e","tid":1699944,"uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T01:59:09.000Z","msg":"捉鬼記（分享）<br />\n2019年11月10日<br />\n<br />\n紅磡沾仔記：好開心科技大學周同學22歲仔死得咁早！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1702629\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1702629</a><br />\n<br />\n又有鬼（港獨之父 #42246）分享假FB，結果今次俾ピピみ絲打fact check知道係假FB，以圖煽動連登巴絲暴力對待沾仔記。<br />\n<br />\n是日精選金句：<br />\n#44 特色主義：&quot;但好多人唔帶腦上連登&quot;<br />\n<br />\n絲打捉鬼記：成功"}]}